930
00:56:44,868 --> 00:56:47,666
Chết tiệt.
Tôi xin lỗi. Xin lỗi.

931
00:56:51,808 --> 00:56:52,832
Này!

932
00:56:53,243 --> 00:56:54,904
Anh đánh rơi cái này.

933
00:56:55,512 --> 00:56:57,002
Ồ, cảm ơn nhé.

934
00:57:03,954 --> 00:57:05,046
